    "long_instructions": "# Expressions\r\n\r\nIn this **Modify** level, you will create an expression that converts human years into dog years. \r\n\r\n::: details [**✅ Step 1**]\r\nCreate an expression that converts human years into dog years and saves that value into a new variable.\r\n:::\r\n\r\n::: details [**✅ Step 2**]\r\nCreate a `print()` statement that lists the name of the dog and its age in dog years.\r\n:::\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n::: details [**🔎 Show me how**]\r\n![](https://images.code.org/0a06fe8720ad83131f079a8266df2904-image-1731966860574.png)\r\n![](https://images.code.org/60dbf035cc293e194378c25a591725e9-image-1731967049191.png)\r\n:::\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nAfter you finish the steps and press `Run` a continue box will appear. ",
